---
title: Seared Steak & Charred Nectarine Salad with Feta, Pecans, and Basil
description: A quick flash in a hot pan transforms juicy nectarines from sweet to nearly candy-like. Tossed with perfectly seared steak, tangy feta, and summery basil, this salad is bound to become a part of your weekly repertoire.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/55ae873dfd2cb958068b4568.jpg
